titles.title: An original resolution authorizing expenditures by the Committee on Agriculture, Nutrition, and Forestry.

calendar.text: Committee on Agriculture, Nutrition, and Forestry ordered to be reported an original measure.

action.text: Committee on Agriculture, Nutrition, and Forestry. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Chambliss. Without written report.
Referred to the Committee on Rules and Administration.

bill.summary: 1/26/2005--Reported to Senate without amendment. Authorizes expenditures by the Committee on Agriculture, Nutrition, and Forestry for the 109th Congress.
